KabatApplicationRecord.description: Kabat was applied to this strip tobacco product at a calculated average rate of 6.2 ppm for the effective control of the Cigarette Beetle (Lasioderma serricorne). Kabat, a registered trademark of Zoecon, Inc. Dallas, Texas, is a 5% w/w formulation of methoprene (active ingredient) and 95% ethanol.
KabatApplicationRecord.calculatedAverageRatePpmFormula: Kabat used mls. X 103.1 (lbs. or 46.8 kgs.) assuming 12.35 OV
